{"results":[{"aya":"015","id":3803,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"他们说：这个只是明显的魔术。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"016","id":3804,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"难道我们死后，已变为尘土和朽骨的时候，必定复活吗？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"017","id":3805,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"连我们的祖先，也要复活吗？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"018","id":3806,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"你说：是的！你们都要卑贱的复活。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"019","id":3807,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"才听见一声呐喊，他们就瞻望着，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"020","id":3808,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":". 他们说：伤哉我们！这就是报应之日。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"021","id":3809,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":". 这就是你们所否认的判决之日。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":26,"previousPage":"/zh/s037-2.json","nextPage":"/zh/s037-4.json"}}